title: Samsung Galaxy Tab A 2016 10.1" Review
description:
Note: the tablet has 2GB RAM and 16GB of storage - I mistakenly refer to 16GB RAM in the video! Also The resolution is 1920 x1200 as described in article below- not 1920x1080.

This video is an overview of the tablet so you can get to see it in use. For a full review and conclusions please see our website:

http://thetechnologyman.com/samsung-galaxy-tab-a-10-1-2016-review/
